1. *Ispravno* je otići kući. (It is correct to go home.)
2. *Ispravna* je odluka da se vrate. (The decision to return is correct.)
3. *Ispravnost* je vrednost koja se ceni. (Correctness is a value that is appreciated.)
4. Oni su se postarali da sve bude *ispravno*. (They took care to make sure everything was right.)
5. *Ispravan* odgovor je bitan za polaganje ispita. (The right answer is important for passing the exam.)